<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">致毕业生</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">亲爱的2024届毕业生：</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.28571em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">你们好！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.28571em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">随着毕业典礼的落幕，你们即将踏上新的征程，开启人生新的篇章。在这个特殊的时刻，校友之家衷心地向你们表示最热烈的祝贺和最美好的祝愿！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240705/1720190976230056169.jpg" title="1720190976230056169.jpg" alt="1720190976230056169.jpg" width="600" height="349" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px; height: 349px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>解锁新身份</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2.28571em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">你们曾是校园里的佼佼者，是知识的追求者，是梦想的实践者。你们用汗水和智慧，书写了属于自己的青春篇章。如今，你们即将离开熟悉的校园，走向更广阔的天地，从此便解锁了一个新的身份——校友。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.28571em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">作为校友，你们将肩负起更多的责任和使命。你们将用所学所得，为社会做出更大的贡献，为母校增添更多的光彩。你们将成为母校与社会之间的桥梁和纽带，传递着母校的精神和文化，也传递着社会的需求和期待。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2.28571em; caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">同时，我们也希望你们能够积极参与校友会的活动，与校友们交流互动，共同分享成功和喜悦。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.28571em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2.28571em; caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">校友之家作为各位校友共同的精神家园和联络纽带，始终秉持着联络校友、服务校友、服务母校的宗旨，致力于推动校友与母校之间的深度合作与共同发展，竭诚为广大校友提供全面、周到、细致的服务。欢迎2024届校友加入各地方校友分会大家庭中！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240705/1720191117203016771.png" title="1720191117203016771.png" alt="1720191117203016771.png" width="600" height="432" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px; height: 432px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>加入我们</strong><br/></p><p></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2.28571em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">山水有相逢，来日皆可期。衷心祝愿各位2024届毕业生们一帆风顺，前程似锦！欢迎各位校友闲暇之余回校共聚，母校的大门永远为你们打开！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2.28571em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 0em; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">联系方式</strong></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">校友办曾星明：15879092133</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &qu